{"tid":759710,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《熱血最強》動畫播放25周年!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-07-29T01:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T07:18:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39cc5bcb81714f0050a15c01f86f984c56785d09","tid":759710,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:23:35.000Z","msg":"Lawton<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-07-28-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.45.58-668x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-07-28-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25885.45.58-668x900.png&h=99883390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為慶祝動畫《熱血最強》播放 25 周年，Bandai Spirits 決定在超級機械人 HG 系列發售《熱血最強》變形合體機械人，可從修羅噴射機分離成馬赫翼龍、大地劍龍、轟天雷龍，再合體成為哥修羅。"},{"pid":"3fbde160727bc64c452a3513d93dfb09e0caedf3","tid":759710,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"今次超級機械人 HG 系列的《熱血最強》機械人，用到 Snap-fit 接合方法，毋須特別加黏合劑，包括馬赫翼龍（マッハプテラ）、大地劍龍（ランドステゴ）、轟天雷龍（サンダーブラキオ）等 3 種動畫內的恐龍機械人，可以合體變形至哥修羅、修羅噴射機。比例則為 1／300。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHG 1/300 GO-SAURER 將會在 2018 年 12 月開始發售，價格為 5,616 日元（連稅，折換港幣約HK$398）。在 Bandai Spirits 自家開發者網誌中，可看到機械人詳細參照以往的設定開發。"},{"pid":"457c05651248ad0dea980bf7eecf9a215b583d01","tid":759710,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:33:35.000Z","msg":"細個好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1bb3bed76570cec08be1ce59edbcc10af1cd1d","tid":759710,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"第四部又係出緊書?<br />\n<br />\n有生之年系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8789866b37cdb742851912bd3f86d05364980b","tid":759710,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,